<headline>Heat Advisory issued July 10 at 2:47PM CDT until July 11 at 9:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 2 PM TO 9 PM CDT TUESDAY...
* WHAT...Heat index values up to 105 expected.
* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon County.
* WHEN...From 2 PM to 9 PM CDT Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, wear light colored clothing, and limit
strenuous activities to the early morning.</instruction>
